    "locked": false,
    "maintainer_can_modify": false,
    "title": "policy: fix negative CFeeRate::ToString() formatting",
    "user": {
      "login": "joaonevess",
      "id": 49655948,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ5NjU1OTQ4",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/49655948?v=4",
      "gravatar_id": "",
      "url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess",
      "html_url": "https://github.com/joaonevess",
      "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/followers",
      "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/following%7B/other_user%7D",
      "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/gists%7B/gist_id%7D",
      "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/starred%7B/owner%7D%7B/repo%7D",
      "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/subscriptions",
      "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/orgs",
      "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/repos",
      "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/events%7B/privacy%7D",
      "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/joaonevess/received_events",
      "type": "User",
      "site_admin": false,
      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "`CFeeRate` may represent modified/effective fee rates, for example after a negative `prioritisetransaction` fee delta.\r\n\r\nPreviously, `CFeeRate::ToString()` formatted the quotient and remainder directly. For negative values, C++ `%` produces a negative remainder, which could result in malformed strings such as `0.-01 sat/vB`.\r\n\r\nThis changes formatting to emit the sign once and format non-negative quotient/remainder parts. Positive fee rate formatting is unchanged.\r\n\r\nThis is a display-only change and does not affect fee calculation or policy behavior.\r\n\r\nIncludes unit test coverage for negative fee rates, including a whole-plus-fractional BTC/kvB value and the `CAmount` minimum value.\r\n\r\nTesting:\r\n- `build-coretest/bin/test_bitcoin --run_test=amount_tests/ToStringTest`\r\n- `build-coretest/bin/test_bitcoin`\r\n- `git diff --check`",
    "labels": [
